Text: Welcome to OnePass Silver Elite MR JOHN GRIFFITHMR JOHN GRIFFITH Congratulations On behalf of everyone at Continental Airlines welcome to the OnePass Silver Elite program Your benefits and privileges are effective March through February Your card and credentials will be mailed to you on or before March To review all of your privileges visit wwwcontinentalcomeliteguide Thank you for making Continental your airline of choice Its always a pleasure to have you fly with us and we hope you enjoy your OnePass Silver membership Sincerely Mark Bergsrud Vice President Marketing FE UNFORTUNATELY MAIL SENT TO THIS ADDRESS CANNOT BE ANSWERED PLEASE DIRECT ALL INQUIRIES TO OAIRCOM Note To modify your OnePass email preferences please login to Your Account at wwwonepasscomyouraccount To unsubscribe from all OnePass email programs please visit wwwonepasscomaspemailunsubscribeframeasp IMAGE
